---
title: Buffalo Meatball Sub with Ragin' Bacon Nachos & Herby Tomato Salsa
description: This loaded sub has incredible flavour to match its incredible size. Coated in a saucy mixture of onion, sriracha and BBQ sauce, you'll never have meatballs any other way again!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/buffalo-meatball-sub-d17b7b25.jpg
